r HLSL stripping / shader-model rollback / hardcoded fixes. Architecture: D3DReflect each VS bytecode post-compile to capture input signature (filter SV_*); install-time 16-byte zero-filled BIND_VERTEX_BUFFER as phantom slot 15 buffer; VertexBufferDescriptorMap augments format-derived elements with phantom InputSlot=15 entries for missing non-SV semantics; StateCache binds phantom buffer at slot 15 with stride=0 before every draw. Per CODEX Q5 the c0000005 access violation (hair_s40 load) is NOT assumed to share root cause; will resolve OR scope to Iter-2 with real stack capture. Iteration target: 1. Risk profile: zero BSOD (pure CPU + 1 install-time GPU buffer). autonomous:false; Kenny smoke validates avatar geometry visible. CODEX consult preserved at 11-09.8-CODEX-CONSULT-texcoord2-signature-mismatch.md. — requirements D3D11-02, D3D11-03
